  "title": {
    "zh": "前翼涡流与 Y-250",
    "en": "Front-wing vortices and the Y-250"
  },
  "summary": {
    "zh": "前翼是 F1 赛车气流的「总开关」。2017—2021 年的复杂多片前翼在鼻锥两侧制造著名的 Y-250 涡流，沿底板边缘一路向后「密封」下压力；2022 年规则把它简化为与鼻锥相连的几片。",
    "en": "The front wing is the 'master switch' of an F1 car's airflow. The complex 2017-2021 wings generated the famed Y-250 vortex along the floor edges to seal downforce; 2022 rules simplified it into nose-connected elements."
  },
  "sourceIds": ["source-book-f1-illustrated-engineering"],
  "updatedAt": "2026-07-14T12:00:00.000Z",
  "category": "aerodynamics",
